fr:mainmatter.html:p:
Now we can rewrite d\mathbf {Q} and d\mathbf {K} as

  d\mathbf {Q}_{i} = \sum _{j} \frac {\exp  \left (\mathbf {Q}_{i} \cdot  \mathbf {K}_{j}\right )}{\mathbf {L}_{i}} \cdot  (d\mathbf {O}_{i}^T \mathbf {V}_j - \mathbf {D}_i) \mathbf {K}_{j}

and

  d\mathbf {K}_{j} = \sum _{j} \frac {\exp  \left (\mathbf {Q}_{i} \cdot  \mathbf {K}_{j}\right )}{\mathbf {L}_{i}} \cdot  (d\mathbf {O}_{i}^T \mathbf {V}_j - \mathbf {D}_i) \mathbf {Q}_{i}

