fr:mainmatter.html:div:
Algorithm. 
while true:

Count occurences of byte pairs. Store in dict D with \{(b_1, b_2): \text {count}\}

Find (b_1, b_2) with highest count.

Merge (b_1, b_2) by (b_{1}, b_{2}) \mapsto  b'

Replace all instances of (b_{1}, b_{2}) in string with b' i.e. 
  b_{1} b_{2} b_{3} b_{4} \mapsto  b'b_{3} b_{4}

